        },
        {
            "title": "爆一爆｜恒生盤數有幾醜？阿媽滙豐要增資（Louise）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"恒生作為持牌銀行，都要向金管局交出年報。 (Photo by Sawayasu Tsuji/Getty Images)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DxVR3ZBMa.et1bP3sXk04g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/fcd53f20-24cf-11f1-b9eb-8bc960b363e5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">恒生作為持牌銀行，都要向金管局交出年報。 (Photo by Sawayasu Tsuji/Getty Images)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上月滙豐（0005.HK）公佈業績時，市場一片唱好，股價攀上＄148高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年火速被阿媽私有化的恒生銀行，盤帳已經納入滙豐入面，當時未知醜婦有幾醜，但恒生作為持牌銀行，都要向金管局交出年報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"affiliate_link\",\"yAffiliateService\":\"other\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"shop-now\",\"ySellerName\":\"Yahoo\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":true}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yfinance.onelink.me/3068494570?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[…]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub3=&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">恒生年報數據亮點</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">揭開恒生嘅面紗，真係「豆皮忟雞」咁好醜怪。每股盈利跌14.8%、 淨息差由2024年2.2%跌至1.99%。商業房地產（CRE）信貸損失達到80億，較2024年升69%，當然派俾阿媽滙豐嘅股息每股$6.8就無變。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b293c10b-6ba2-4528-b519-5913bc030434-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒生衰喺商業房地產已街知巷聞，但到底有幾大鑊？年報披露整體上嘅CRE信貸進一步出現負面轉移，即係質素愈來愈差。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒生把信貸質素分為五級，最大鑊嘅屬有信貸損失（credit impaired），由2024年$198億上升至2025年嘅$269億。這堆有信貸損失嘅貸款，其貸款成數loan-to-value達到74%，即是件磚頭秤到值100蚊，恒生就借74蚊，商業房地產點止跌咗三成呢？咁想唔輸入肉都唔得啦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恒生咁醜，咪話唔影響到阿媽滙豐，近排滙豐股價由高位$148蚊跌咗近18%，除咗中東打仗之外，恒生呢個衰仔唔生性都係有關嘅，對阿媽嘅資本肯定有影響。本週三滙豐就公佈發行兩筆25億美元嘅永久後償或可轉換證券，以加強銀行資本基礎，息率有成6.75%至7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現時匯豐息率4.7厘左右，啲滙豐大戶現時係除淨後，大可沽貨套現換碼，於下週三開始認購呢批高息票據，咁睇的話，滙豐股價似乎都未跌夠。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%88%86%E4%B8%80%E7%88%86%EF%BD%9C%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E7%9B%A4%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%86%9C%EF%BC%9F%E9%98%BF%E5%AA%BD%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E8%A6%81%E5%A2%9E%E8%B3%87%EF%BC%88louise%EF%BC%89-024844134.html",
